rows.label: tlk70000013_01_msg0001
rows.name:
All sorts live here in this city, but
everyone carries their own worries
around, and that makes us all alike.

rows.label: tlk70000013_01_msg0002
rows.name:
If someone came and asked you for
help you'd hear them out, eh? That's
because you can empathize with them.

rows.label: tlk70000013_01_msg0003
rows.name:
That empathy is something the people
you help will never forget. They'll
support you, rain or shine.

rows.label: tlk70000013_01_msg0004
rows.name:
On top of that, once you make a name
for yourself, new doors open up on
account of your rep.

rows.label: tlk70000013_01_msg0005
rows.name:
But don't let that fame go to your head.
And never think of others as smaller
than yourself. It only causes pain.

rows.label: tlk70000013_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Remember that and the bonds you
make will stay with you throughout
your life.
